writer.name: 史蒂文·卡纳尔斯 Steven Canals

introduction: ABC has put in development In The End, a drama from Pose co-creator Steven Canals and his Story Ave. Productions, and 20th Television, where Canals is under a deal.Written and executive produced by Canals, centers on Kiona Brown, who, incapable of living life to the fullest, makes the only logical choice – to embrace death as an end-of-life doula. With an eclectic list of patients – including cancer survivor Mariana Cortez – Kiona soon discovers the secret to a new beginning is to embrace what happens…in the end.
